## My recommendation for **NEXT IMPLEMENTATION**

Not JWT.

Not React.

Not websocket.

Not backtesting.

Do:

# Trade + Portfolio Engine

Because everything you listed depends on it.

Dependency chain:

```text
Trades
↓
Portfolio
↓
Automation
↓
Strategies
↓
Backtesting
↓
Broker execution
↓
Dashboard/Websocket
```

We can start implementing this **properly**:

```text
trade/entity/Trade.java
trade/service/TradeService.java
POST /trade/buy
POST /trade/sell
GET /portfolio/{userId}
```

using your existing package structure.




